notesStmt.note: Only European Community legislation printed in the paper edition of the Official Journal of the European Union is deemed authentic.

body.p: Amendment to the list of spirituous beverages in Annex II to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1576/89 (1), the minimum alcoholic strength of which as determined by national laws is higher than the values laid down in the Community regulations for the category to which they belong
Published pursuant to Article 3 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1576/89
(Official Journal of the European Communities No C 1 of 4 January 1990, page 14)
